{"id":669,"type":4,"name":"Mirror's Edge","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/5c/04/669_Lqc5c.jpg","rating":{"total":281,"count":{"1":2,"2":0,"3":1,"4":1,"5":7,"6":46,"7":100,"8":79,"9":38,"10":7},"score":7.3},"summary":"　　《镜之边缘》是一款由EA DICE开发，并由美国艺电发行的第一人称动作冒险游戏，这也是史上第一款以跑酷为题材制作的电子游戏。该游戏於2008年11月在PlayStation 3和Xbox 360的平台发行，Windows版本则在2009年1月13日发行。\r\n\r\n　　这款游戏公布於2007年7月10日，采用虚幻引擎3（Unreal Engine 3），并增加了由DICE相关的照明试验室开发的照明新解决方案。游戏不止色泽鲜艳，而且不同於其他大多数第一人称游戏的是它拥有更多的动作（如攀墙、飞檐走壁、撞门、过独木桥、荡动、爬水管、荡绳、翻滚等），以及更大的活动自由，例如没有平视显示器（HUD），而且角色的腿部、手臂和躯干在屏幕上是可见的。\r\n\r\n　　游戏背景设定在一个言论被极权政府重度监控的社会，而包括主角绯丝（Faith）在内的“信使”（runner）网络则被用来逃避政府监督以传递信息。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>镜之边缘</li><li><span>开发: </span>EA、<a href=\"/person/18591\">EA DICE</a></li><li><span>发行: </span><a href=\"/person/13930\">Electronic Arts</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>暗镜迷踪</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>靓影特务</li><li><span>平台: </span>Windows Phone</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>iOS</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PC</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>Xbox 360</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PS3</li><li><span>游戏类型: </span>AAVG / Platform</li><li><span>游戏引擎: </span>虚幻引擎3</li><li><span>游玩人数: </span>单人</li><li><span>发行日期: </span>2008年11月11日</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>http://www.mirrorsedge.com/</li>","collection":{"wish":48,"collect":317,"doing":10,"on_hold":34,"dropped":35},"tags":[{"name":"跑酷","count":66},{"name":"EA","count":64},{"name":"ACT","count":54},{"name":"PC","count":43},{"name":"东西审美大对决","count":17},{"name":"镜之边缘","count":15},{"name":"Edge","count":13},{"name":"XBOX360","count":10},{"name":"晕3D","count":8},{"name":"STEAM","count":7},{"name":"美如画","count":7},{"name":"DICE","count":6},{"name":"FPS","count":5},{"name":"Mirror","count":5},{"name":"IOS","count":4},{"name":"2009","count":2},{"name":"AAVG","count":2},{"name":"PS3","count":2},{"name":"Platform","count":2},{"name":"2008","count":2},{"name":"好喜欢那副手套"